                  -----------
                   DVDStyler
                  -----------
About
-------
DVDStyler is a cross-platform free DVD authoring application that makes
possible for video enthusiasts to create professional-looking DVDs.

License
-------
DVDStyler is free software. You may use it for any personal, commercial or
educational purpose, including installing it on as many different computers
as you wish. DVDStyler is licensed under the GNU General Public License (GPL).

See http://www.dvdstyler.org for more information
